      <title>中国刺激计划为各大银行定下基调，汇丰全力改革</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/china-stimulus-sets-tone-for-major-banks-hsbc-is-all-about-overhaul</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国最近推出的经济刺激措施将为中国工商银行股份有限公司、中国建设银行股份有限公司、中国农业银行股份有限公司和中国银行股份有限公司等主要中国银行业金融机构第三季度的盈利情况定下基调。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/china-stimulus-sets-tone-for-major-banks-hsbc-is-all-about-overhaul</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 02:05:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国在创纪录降息后仍未下调政策利率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/china-refrains-from-cutting-policy-rate-following-record-trim</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国央行在一个月前将融资成本大幅下调至历史最高水平后，维持一年期政策利率不变，表明当局正谨慎推进货币刺激政策以支持经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/china-refrains-from-cutting-policy-rate-following-record-trim</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 01:29:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>关键融资成本上升，中国银行面临流动性困境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/chinese-banks-face-liquidity-struggle-as-key-funding-cost-rises</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国银行的融资压力正在加大，这是货币宽松政策加大引发股市上涨、债务产品需求减少的意外后果。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/chinese-banks-face-liquidity-struggle-as-key-funding-cost-rises</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 01:10:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>比亚迪出口前景是其下一阶段 66% 强劲增长的关键</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/byd-s-export-outlook-key-to-next-phase-of-66-peer-beating-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[市场已然预期中国汽车制造商比亚迪股份有限公司的销量将创下纪录，因此，需要一个令人信服的海外增长故事来刺激其股价再创涨势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/byd-s-export-outlook-key-to-next-phase-of-66-peer-beating-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 01:05:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新加坡房价跌幅小于预期；租金反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/singapore-home-prices-fall-less-than-expected-rents-rebound</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新加坡第三季度房价跌幅低于预期，因为 9 月底新房销售热潮抵消了跌幅，而租金则自 2023 年以来首次上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/singapore-home-prices-fall-less-than-expected-rents-rebound</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 00:37:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>名厨有望在韩国 IPO 中获利 1.8 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/culinary-class-wars-judge-to-boost-korea-s-ipo-market-with-61-million-listing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位凭借 Netflix 热门节目而出名的厨师准备推动韩国陷入困境的 IPO 市场，他将把他的连锁餐厅上市，这笔交易可能让他所持的股份价值达到约 1.8 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/culinary-class-wars-judge-to-boost-korea-s-ipo-market-with-61-million-listing</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 00:14:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本央行行长加藤在加强警告后与耶伦讨论外汇问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/japan-s-kato-discusses-fx-with-yellen-after-ramping-up-warnings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本财务大臣加藤胜信与美国总统耶伦讨论了外汇市场的发展情况，此前一天，加藤胜信加强了对日元快速下跌的警告。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/japan-s-kato-discusses-fx-with-yellen-after-ramping-up-warnings</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 00:01:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲股市波动，债券收益率下降：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一些亚洲股市基准指数上涨，美国国债收益率下降提振了市场人气。日元走强后，日本股市表现不佳。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 24 Oct 2024 22:30:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>凯雷支持的理学株式会社在东京首次公开募股时的交易价格低于 IPO 价格</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/carlyle-backed-rigaku-to-debut-as-japan-s-ipo-rush-gains-pace</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管理学控股公司 (Rigaku Holdings Corp.) 的发行结果表明投资者对在繁忙的一级市场上进行大型日本股票交易仍有兴趣，但该公司的股价在首次公开募股时仍下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/carlyle-backed-rigaku-to-debut-as-japan-s-ipo-rush-gains-pace</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 24 Oct 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
